    "title": "Now Hiring Logistics Manager at Ceva Logistics India Capital India",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Ceva Logistics India Capital India. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Logistics Manager to strengthen our Lucknow-based team.\n\nAbout Ceva Logistics India Capital India:\nCeva Logistics India Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ceva Logistics India Capital India!",
